To install do the following  : 

Pre-requisites : 
python
numpy
scipy
scikit-learn
nose for testing

Installation of prerequisites : 



Installation of source:

$ cd /path/to/ssystem/root/directory
$ python setup.py build
$ python setup.py install


For dev and test
$ cd /path/to/ssystem/root/directory
$ python setup.py build_ext --inplace
$ nosetests
